text: Sökmen is a Turkish given name or surname. Notable persons with that name include: * Sökmen (Artuqid) (died 1104), Turkish bey * Sökmen el-Kutbî (died 1111), Turkish bey * Sökmen II (died 1185), Turkish ruler * Ayhan Sökmen (1929–2013), Turkish physician * Tayfur Sökmen (1892–1980), Turkish politician Category:Turkish-language surnames
